obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line 1
  line `THE PREVENTION OF MONEY - LAUNDERING ACT, 2002`
  line __________
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line __________
  line `CHAPTER I`
  line `P RELIMINARY`
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title, extent and commencement.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `CHAPTER II`
  line `O FFENCE OF M ONEY - L AUNDERING`
  line `3. Offence of money - laundering.`
  line `4. Punishment for money - laundering.`
  line `CHAPTER III`
  line `A TTACHMENT, A DJUDICATION AND C ONFISCATION`
  line `5. Attachment of property involved in money - laundering.`
  line `6. Adjudicating Authorities, composition, power s, etc.`
  line `7. Staff of Adjudicating Authorities.`
  line `8. Adjudication.`
  line `9. Vesting of property in Central Government.`
  line `10. Management of properties confiscated under this Chapter.`
  line `11. Power regarding summons, production of documents and evidence, etc.`
  line `CHAPTER IV`
  line `O BLIGATIONS OF B ANKING C OMPANIES, F INANCIAL I NSTITUTIONS AND I NTERMEDIARIES`
  line `11A. Verification of identity by reporting entity.`
  line `12. Reporting entity to maintain records.`
  line `12A. Access to information.`
  line `12AA. Enhanced due diligence.`
  line `13. Power s of Director to impose fine.`
  line `14. No civil or criminal proceedings against reporting entity, its directors and employees in certain`
  line cases.
  line `15. Procedure and manner of furnishing information by reporting entities.`
  line `CHAPTER V`
  line `S UMMONS, S EARCHES AND S EIZURES, ETC.`
  line `16. Power of survey.`
  line `17. Search and seizure.`
  line `18. Search of persons.`
