obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line 5
  line `1 [( ha ) ” client ” means a person who is engaged in a financial transaction or activity with a reporting`
  line `entity and includes a person on whose behalf the person who engaged in the trans action or activity, is`
  line acting;]
  line `( i ) “ co - operative bank ” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in clause ( dd ) of section 2`
  line `of the Deposit Insurance and Credit Guarantee Corp oration Act, 1961 (47 of 1961);`
  line `1 [( ia ) ” corresponding law ” means any law of any foreign country corresponding to any of the`
  line `provisio ns of this Act or dealing with offences in that country corresponding to any of the scheduled`
  line offences;
  line `(ib) ” dealer ” has the same meaning as assigned to it in clause (b) of section 2 of the`
  line `Central Sales Tax Act, 1956 (74 of 1956);]`
  line `( j ) “ Deputy Director ” means a Deputy Director appointed under sub - section ( 1 ) of section 49;`
  line `2 * * * * *`
  line `( k ) “ Director ” or “ Additional Director ” or “ Joint Director ” means a Director or Additional`
  line `Director or Joint Director, as the case may be, appointed under sub - section ( 1 ) of section 49;`
  line `3 [( l ) “ financial institution ” means a financial institution as defined in clause (c) of section 45 - 1 of`
  line `the Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934 (2 of 1934) and includes a chit fund company, a housing finance`
  line `institution, an authorised person, a payment system operator, a non - banking financial company and`
  line `the Department of Posts in the Government of India;]`
  line `( m ) “ housing finance institution ” shall have the meaning as assigned to it in clause ( d ) of`
  line `section 2 of the National Housi ng Bank Act, 1987 (53 of 1987);`
  line `4 [ ( n ) “ intermediary ” means, —`
  line `( i ) a stock - broker, 5 *** share transfer agent, banker to an issue, trustee to a trust deed,`
  line `registrar to an issue, merchant banker, underwriter, portfolio manager, investment adviser or any`
  line `other intermediary associated with securities market and registered under section 12 of th e`
  line `Securities and Exchange Board of India Act, 1992 (15 of 1992); or`
  line `( ii ) an association recognised or registered under the Forward Contracts (Regulation)`
  line `Act, 1952 (74 of 1952) or any member of such association; or`
  line `( iii ) intermediary registered by t he Pension Fund Regulatory and Development Authority; or`
  line `( iv ) a recognised stock e xchange referred to in clause ( f ) of section 2 of the Securities`
  line `Contracts (Regulation) Act, 1956 (42 of 1956);]`
  line `6 [( na ) “ investigation ” includes all the proceedings under this Act conducted by the Director or by`
  line `an authority authorised by the Central Government under this Act fo r the collection of evidence;]`
  line `( o ) “ Member ” means a Member of the Appellate Tribuna l and includes the Chairperson;`
  line `( p ) “ money - laundering ” has the meani ng assigned to it in section 3;`
  line `( q ) “ non - banking financial company ” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in clause ( f )`
  line `of section 45 - I of the Reserve Bank of In dia Act, 1934 (2 of 1934) 7 ***;`
  line `( r ) “ n otification ” means a notification pub lished in the Official Gazette;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 2 of 2013, s. 2 (w.e.f. 15 - 2 - 2013).`
  line `2. Clause ( ja ) o mitted by s. 2, ibid. (w.e.f. 15 - 2 - 2013).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 2, ibid., for clause ( l ) (w.e.f. 15 - 2 - 2013).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 2, ibid., for clause ( n ) (w.e.f. 15 - 2 - 2013).`
  line `5. The word “sub - broker,” omitted by Act 23 of 2019, s. 192 (w.e.f. 1 - 8 - 2019).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 20 of 2005, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1 - 7 - 2005).`
  line `7. The words “and includes a person carrying on designated business or profession” omitted by Act 2 of 2013, s. 2`
  line `(w.e.f. 15 - 2 - 2013).`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
