obj_root_law_sections_37_content:
  string
  line 37
  line `75. Power to remove dif ficulties. — ( 1 ) If any difficulty arises in giving effect to the provisions of`
  line `this Act, the Central Government may, by order, published in the Official Gazette, make such provisions`
  line `not inconsistent with the provisions of this Act a s may appear to be neces sary for removing the difficulty:`
  line `Provided that no order shall be made under this section after the expiry of two years fro m the`
  line `commencement of this Act.`
  line `( 2 ) Every order made under this section shall be laid, as soon as may be after it is made, before each`
  line `House of Parliament.`
