  line `be Government property.`
  line `51 read with section 44 Contravention of provisions of section 44 relating to dealings in trophy`
  line `and animal articles without licence prohibited.`
  line `51 read with section 48 Contravention of provisions of section 48 relating to purchase of animal,`
  line `etc., by licensee.`
  line `51 read with sec tion 49B Contravention of provisions of section 49B relating to prohibition of`
  line `dealings in trophies, animals articles, etc., derived from scheduled animals.`
